                <statement>
                    <p>Suppose you need to plot the equation <m>x=3.14</m>. You decide to try making a table of points. Fill out some points for this table.</p>

                    <sidebyside>
                        <tabular>
                            <row bottom="medium" halign="center">
                                <cell><m>x</m></cell>
                                <cell><m>y</m></cell>
                            </row>
